{"word":"H520 - אַמָּה - ʼammâh - am-maw' - Cubit","slug":"H520","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אַמָּה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼammâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>am-maw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Cubit"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D0;&#x05DE;&#x05BC;&#x05D4; - 'amma&#x0302;h</b> - <i>am-maw'</i><p/>Prolonged from <a href=\"#/H517\">H517</a>; properly a <i>mother</i> (that is, <i>unit</i>) of measure, or the <i>forearm</i> (below the elbow), that is, a <i>cubit</i>; also a door <i>base</i> (as a <i>bond</i> of the entrance): - cubit, + hundred [by exchange for <a href=\"#/H3967\">H3967</a>], measure, post."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H517\">H517</a>, <a href=\"#/H522\">H522</a>, <a href=\"#/H523\">H523</a>, <a href=\"#/H538\">H538</a>"}]}